  "title": "ISic003411. Tile inscribed with funerary epitaph",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέ<span class=\"error\" title=\"hi tag with rend=stacked is not supported!\">ρᾳ</span></span>  <span data-text=\"Σαββάτου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σάββατον\">Σαβ(βά)τ(ου)</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\"><span data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἰαγάθη</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρᾳ</span>  <span data-text=\"Σαββάτου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σάββατον\">Σαββάτου</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἰαγάθη</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕ<span class=\"error\" title=\"hi tag with rend=stacked is not supported!\">ΡΑ</span></span><span data-text=\"Σαββάτου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σάββατον\">ΣΑΒΤ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\"><span data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">ΙΑΓΑΘΗ</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑ</span><span data-text=\"Σαββάτου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σάββατον\">ΣΑΒΒΑΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰαγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">ΙΑΓΑΘΗ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Ferrua 1989</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Iagathe, on the day of the sabbath</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The difficulty of reading this text means that there are multiple alternative readings and some intepret the cross as a menorah and so read this as a Jewish text instead.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Fiorelli NSA 1880 36 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1961 197 fig.22 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.474 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li><li> Wessel 1989 246 no. 1055 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 2004-2005 364 fig.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003134\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003134</a>  </li><li> Muscolino 2011-2012 229 G17 fig.12 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-2  17  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
